          <p class="text-stone-600">Sound professional even when customers are angry about missed flights or lost reservations. Feel confident in every response.</p>
          <%= image_tag "social-serenity.svg", class: "w-full max-w-xs mx-auto mt-6", alt: "Stay calm under pressure" %>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-20 bg-gradient-to-t from-white to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-stone-200">
