          <p class="text-stone-600">VIPReply organizes emails by priority. Always know which emails need attention and which are caught up. No more forgotten customers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-stone-200">
          <div class="bg-purple-100 rounded-full p-6 mb-4 w-24 h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
