            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-stone-800">Get started effortlessly</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">Sign up with Google in one click. No complicated setup, no training required. Start replying faster in under 60 seconds.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
