            <p>"I have been using VIPReply for the last 6 months for an airport parking lot. I used to struggle to be consistent answering customer questions. VIPReply has made the process 10 times easier and more enjoyable."</p>
          </blockquote>
          <figcaption class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-x-6">
            <%= image_tag "cathy_testimonial.jpg", class: "size-12 rounded-full bg-stone-200", alt: "Cathy Testimonial" %>
